biolockj.node.r16s

Class QiimeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • biolockj.node.OtuNodeImpl
      • biolockj.node.r16s.QiimeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OtuNode

    public class QiimeNode
extends OtuNodeImpl
implements OtuNode
    This class holds the OTU assignments from one line of QiimeClassifier output.

    2 sample lines (header + 1st row) from otu_table_L*.txt output by QIIME script: "summarize_taxa.py"
    # Constructed from biom file #OTU ID 3A.1 7A.1 120A.1
    7A.1 k__Bacteria;p__Actinobacteria 419.0 26.0 90.0 70.0
